title: Mohammad Ameer Sultan wins NA-110 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Mohammad Ameer Sultan won the National Assembly NA-110 Jhang III constituency election by securing 199,590 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz Mohammad Asif Muavia, who bagged 104,171 votes.
Votersâ€™ turn-out remained at 60.58 per cent.
